<h2 class=3D"wp-block-heading">What is a gram?</h2>



<p data-slot-rendered-content=3D"true">A gram is a metric unit of weight, m=
uch smaller than a pound. It=E2=80=99s abbreviated as =E2=80=9Cg=E2=80=9D a=
nd is used worldwide, especially in scientific contexts and countries that =
follow the metric system. Grams are often used to measure smaller quantitie=
s of ingredients in cooking and baking, as well as in pharmaceuticals and o=
ther precise measurements.</p>
